The coding sequence of <termsem="EG:434423"> Esg1 </term> was amplified by PCR with the <termsem="EG:434423"> pH34 </term> - gw-s ( 5 ' - AAAAAGCAGGCTGGATGATGGTGACCCTCGTGA-3 ' ) and <termsem="EG:434423"> pH34 </term> - gw-as ( 5 ' - AGAAAGCTGGGTCTGCATCCAGGTCGGAGACA-3 ' ) primers .
